snippet.title: Cirno Fumo: The Horror Game (Gameplay Trailer)
snippet.description:
Game Link: https://semi9.itch.io/cirno-horror

Cirno Fumo: The Horror Game is small Touhou fangame that revolves around Cirno Fumo.
You wander around in a building to find power, whilst avoiding Cirno Fumo.

It is, quite possibly, the game of all time.
